                  <Text layoutX="30.0" layoutY="115.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Matter is defined as anything that has mass and occupies space. It includes all the materials and substances around us, whether visible like a book or invisible like air. Chemistry, as a science, begins with the study of matter because understanding its nature allows us to comprehend how different substances behave and interact in various environments." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
